700707f-b.title: Bronx: Castle Hill Avenue - Watson Avenue
700707f-b.text:
(1)
Castle Hill Avenue, at the S.W. corner of Watson Avenue, showing
the Holy Family Roman Catholic Church and the rectory. The view is
across E. 177th Street.
July 1, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

(2)
Another view of the rectory and church, viewed south along the
avenue from Blackrock AVenue.
May 1O, 1938.
